idk, isnt that the point though... combat takes away your mobility... clearing wards by yourself is dangerous, its suppose to be.... and safer if you already have vision and are renewing that vision.... so rewards you for good habits like warding and counter warder, and sets you up for death if you (ur team i mean) has been slacking

also, warding during a team fight can be important... {{champion:84}} {{champion:35}} .... not to mention it can ruin an attack move command for your favor, so attacking wards seems to be directly related to combat, which negates the boots for good reason ya?

{{champion:37}}  i understand the pain of lack of mobility, squishyness, and lack of sight, but its suppose to be there for a reason ya? to give the choice of what boots really are better...{{item:3274}}  boots of mobility or maybe u need swiftness instead {{item:3280}} , or maybe go for something else for a diff reason.... {{item:3158}}
